title: Yuusha-sama no Osananajimi to Iu Settei no Make Heroine ni Tensei shita node, Chougoushi ni Job Change Shimasu.
altTitle: Yuusha-sama no Osananajimi to Iu Shokugyou no Make Heroine ni Tensei shita node, Chougoushi ni Job Change Shimasu.
